{
  "stem": "15962.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we pretended that we have a kingdom in northern Canada, in the Western Territories near the Slave Lake.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one of my friends, who was about a year older, had a great imagination and was a real, a talented boy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We read many of the Indian stories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we-- our imagination created this, this kingdom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so when we went to uh, Terezin to this children's-- these, these quarters, he became the editor of, in chief of this magazine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And each of us had the special function.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wrote a story that appeared each, each week-- a portion-- about an Indian and a trappist and about the life in the, in the Northern Territories there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm now asked, you know, where did I get the ideas, and so on, in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it just comes back few years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were playing in the home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So for, for many, this period in the ghetto was actually a very creative one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there has been a great deal of art.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because artists, musicians, and the, the cream of the society really was concentrated in this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you remember the name of the magazine?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Comrade'-- means friend.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can show you copies of it if you're interested.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had my bar mitzvah up there in June of 1943.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in an attic space.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, it was not legal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just somehow remember my father standing near me but not very much more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was prepared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I was given lessons to prepare for it in advance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was some instruction but not any-- I don't remember attending any other services or holidays per se.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was simply not encouraged.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
